public class Person extends Object

    • viewPersonalDetails

      public String viewPersonalDetails()
      Retrieves the personal details of a person, including their ID, name, age, gender, address, and contact details as a single string.
      Returns:
      a string representation of the person's details composed of personID, name, age, gender, address, and contactDetails fields concatenated with spaces in between.
